<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reflection-n">reflection <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'flekʃn/    美 /rɪ'flekʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 反射：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the reflection of a sound wave 
声波的反射</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 映像：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the <strong>reflection of</strong> the trees in the lake 
湖面映出树的倒影</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 反映：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On some level, a student’s grades <strong>are a reflection on</strong> the teacher. 
在某种程度上，学生的成绩是老师水平的反映。</p></div>

<h4 id="4c-u">4.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 反复思考；仔细考虑</strong></h4></div>